French Guiana, 1913 Dr. Bongrand 
<emphasis id="AB89EAB8FFDAFF96FC07DDF8AC1DF949" box="[1019,1050,1733,1754]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="337">leg</emphasis>
